Is the array sorted?
├─ YES → Likely Opposite Direction
│   ├─ Finding pairs/sums? → Opposite Direction ✓
│   └─ Finding subarrays? → Consider Same Direction
└─ NO → 
    ├─ Need to find cycles/middle? → Fast & Slow ✓
    ├─ Working with subarrays? → Same Direction ✓
    └─ Can sort the array? → Sort first, then Opposite Direction